articles.author: Chris Lau
articles.title: Snorkeler survives crocodile attack by pulling his head from its jaws - CNN
articles.description: An Australian man bitten on the head by a crocodile while snorkeling in the sea off far north Queensland escaped the unusual attack by prizing open the reptile’s jaws.
articles.content:
